name: Element_emptyTest
description: Unit tests for the empty method of the Element class.

test_cases.name: testEmptyWithChildren
test_cases.description: Tests the empty method of the Element class when the element has children. Verifies that the children are removed and their parent nodes are set to null.

test_cases.name: testEmptyWithoutChildren
test_cases.description: Tests the empty method of the Element class when the element has no children. Verifies that the element's child nodes list remains empty.
